column10: This file contains a summary of the daily land-surface average anomaly
% results produced by the Berkeley Earth averaging method.  Temperatures
% are in Celsius and reported as anomalies relative to the Jan 1951-Dec 1980
% The current dataset presented here is described as:
%   Berkeley Earth daily TAVG full dataset
% This current analysis product is preliminary and may be subject to
% Results are based on 50461 monthly time series
%   with 21047039 observations and 48263 daily time series
